premise_source_doc_sentence: He sets these songs to new music and also writes songs about his personal experiences or the lives and struggles of his heroes : Tom Barker , Michael Davitt , Mother Jones , Douglas Mawson , Raoul Wallenberg , and Emiliano Zapata , among others .
Chandrabose  (  composer  )  , Indian composer who writes songs for Kollywood films
Chandrabose  (  lyricist  )  , Indian lyricist who writes songs for Tollywood films
